          'image' => 
          array (
            'file' => 'moneta_da_investimento-2.jpg',
            'alt' => 'numismatic investment, decadrachm of Syracuse',
            'link' => '__ROUTE:guide.faq__',
          ),
          'body' => 'The various minting techniques are also a source of great interest, as they trace the history of one of the first objects to be produced “industrially”. If you wish to learn more, visit the page <a href="__ROUTE:guide.intro_numismatica__">An introduction to numismatics and collecting</a>. All these aspects make coins and banknotes highly sought after; they are exchanged and traded frequently, establishing values that in some cases are extremely high. It is not unusual to hear of collection coins regarded as investment opportunities, so much so that banks and investment funds include them in their portfolios; in particular, during periods of economic crisis they are proposed again as interesting alternative investments. Before undertaking a numismatic investment, it is advisable to consult a knowledgeable adviser, who may also be an established professional. In any case, certain considerations must not be overlooked; if they are not taken on board, they can nullify the financial effort.',
        ),
        2 => 
