          'body' => '<b style="text-align: left;">Return on investment</b> - Prudent purchases protect the investment from currency devaluations and the uncertainty of financial markets. Over the long term the result is certainly very interesting, but even over the medium term it can normally be considered appreciable; it becomes particularly attractive in periods of severe economic or financial crisis.<br><br><b>Management</b> - The costs of storing numismatic objects are minimal; a small safe-deposit box or a home safe together with an insurance policy are all that is needed, along with a few precautions regarding the chosen environment: generally low humidity, and for banknotes attention to continuous, direct exposure to light sources.',
