          'answer' => 'It\'s a rare modern coin realized in the United States of America. It\'s a silver copy  with the value of a dollar minted in 1974 and sold in June 2010 in a private transaction in United States for $ 7.850.000, approximately 6.488.000 euros. To be honest the most expensive coin would be a gold copy, from the United States, of 20 dollars minted in 1933. In July 2002 it was bought in New York at Sotheby\'s for 7.600.000 dollars, commissions of the auction house included (at that time approximately 7.500.000 euros).',
