          'body' => 'We propose here a brief summary of coins that acquired particular approval and value also out of their borders, becoming coins of international interest.<br><br>

The tetradrachm or Athenian Owl<br>The stater or "Pegasus" of Corinth<br>The tetradrachm of Alexander the Great<br>The roman denarius of republican era<br>The roman denarius of imperial era<br>The roman aureus<br>The byzantine solidus<br>The florin<br>The venetian ducat<br>The thaler<br>The leeuwenndaalder<br>The Spanish coin of 8 escudos<br>The Spanish coin of 8 reals<br>The dollar<br>The marengo<br>The écu of 5 Francs<br>The English Sovereign<br>The euro<br>

